WEBVTT

00:02:59.427 --> 00:03:00.780
Jesu li Velike piramide bile fenomenalne?!

00:03:00.780 --> 00:03:03.030
Da, piramide su bile fenomenalne.

00:03:03.030 --> 00:03:05.176
Grand Canyon. Hajde!

00:03:05.176 --> 00:03:08.404
Star je gotovo 80 milijuna godina.

00:03:08.404 --> 00:03:10.171
Je li Grand Canyon fenomenalan?!

00:03:10.171 --> 00:03:11.712
Da, Grand Canyon jest.

00:03:11.712 --> 00:03:16.470
Louis Daguerre izumio 
je fotografiju 1829.,

00:03:16.470 --> 00:03:17.989
i kad ste danas

00:03:17.989 --> 00:03:19.954
izvukli svoj smartphone,

00:03:19.954 --> 00:03:22.566
i uslikali svoj fenomenalni sendvič...

00:03:22.566 --> 00:03:24.311
Poznajete sebe...

00:03:24.311 --> 00:03:26.527
(Smijeh)

00:03:26.527 --> 00:03:28.867
Nije li to bilo lakše od izlaganja slike

00:03:28.867 --> 00:03:31.443
bakrenim pločama premazanima
jodiranim srebrom?